OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,FAn SDLP councillor has resigned from
OL,7,Fthe party over their handling of the
OL,8,FBobby Sands statue row.
OL,10,FPaul Doherty, who served as deputy
OL,11,Flord mayor of Belfast, and is a
OL,12,Fcouncillor for west Belfast, said he
OL,13,Fknows the statue of the IRA hunger
OL,14,Fstriker "holds real significance".
OL,16,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said their
OL,17,Fcouncillors had faced "an unacceptable
OL,18,Flevel of intimidation", after
OL,19,Fabstaining on a DUP motion in relation
OL,20,Fto the memorial.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@aO]yD@WOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
