FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,FThe statue to Sands, who was 27 when
OL,7,Fhe died on hunger strike in 1981, was
OL,8,Funveiled last year at the Republican
OL,9,FMemorial Garden in Twinbrook, west
OL,10,FBelfast, marking the 44th anniversary
OL,11,Fof the former MP's death.
OL,13,FIt later emerged that it had been
OL,14,Ferected without planning permission,
OL,15,Fthough the council has not previously
OL,16,Ftaken any action.
OL,18,FAt the meeting on Thursday, a DUP
OL,19,Fmotion which called for the matter to
OL,20,Fbe "reconsidered", was passed.
OL,26,@|D@DOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
