OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,FA Sinn Fein amendment seeking a review
OL,7,Fof the "current enforcement status of
OL,8,Fall such structures" across the
OL,9,Fcouncil area was unsuccessful.
OL,11,FMr Doherty posted on social media
OL,12,Foutlining that he has "left the SDLP
OL,13,Fwith immediate effect".
OL,15,F"My focus will remain on the ground in
OL,16,Fmy community, representing the people
OL,17,Fof west Belfast," he said.
OL,26,@oD@HOUpD@TO]tD@WOUuD@VO]wD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
