PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,F"For clarity, I was not at the hastily
OL,7,Farranged Belfast City Council meeting
OL,8,Fthis week ` contrary to some posts
OL,9,Fdirected at me.
OL,11,F"I was dealing with an emerging issue
OL,12,Fin the community and therefore did not
OL,13,Fhave the opportunity to vote against
OL,14,Fthe DUP motion ` which I would have
OL,15,Fdone.
OL,17,F"Anyone suggesting otherwise is simply
OL,18,Ftrying to score cheap political points.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,F"As someone from west Belfast, I know
OL,7,Fthe Bobby Sands statue in Twinbrook
OL,8,Fholds real significance for people in
OL,9,Four community and beyond.
OL,11,F"People should be fully entitled to
OL,12,Fremember him in this way, and I fully
OL,13,Fsupport that. Shame on the DUP and
OL,14,Fothers for turning this into a
OL,15,Fpolitical stunt.
OL,17,F"My focus remains, as always, on the
OL,18,Fpeople of my community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
