PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,FMs Hanna said Mr Doherty "has been a
OL,7,Fvalued representative of the SDLP over
OL,8,Fmany years".
OL,10,F"The SDLP representatives on Belfast
OL,11,FCity Council collectively developed
OL,12,Ftheir position on the Bobby Sands
OL,13,Fstatue. Following the motion, our
OL,14,Fcouncillors were subjected to an
OL,15,Funacceptable level of intimidation,"
OL,16,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@KO]rD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
