OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1777295491
OL,3,CWest Belfast councillor Paul Doherty
OL,4,Cresigns from SDLP
OL,6,F"While the party has sought to support
OL,7,FPaul throughout this period, he has
OL,8,Ftaken the decision to step down, and
OL,9,Fwe respect his decision to put his
OL,10,Ffamily first.
OL,12,F"The SDLP is proud to be committed and
OL,13,Fconsistent on equality, fairness and
OL,14,Frespectful debate. There is no place
OL,15,Ffor intimidation in our politics or
OL,16,Four society.
OL,18,F"We thank Paul for his service and
OL,19,Fwish him and his family every best
OL,20,Fwish for the future."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@UO]
